[*] --> OnHold
OnHold --> Rejected : approve
OnHold : entry / log follower
Rejected --> Delivered : submit
Delivered --> Closed : confirm
Closed --> Reviewed : update
Closed : entry / log follower
Closed --> Delivered : revert
Reviewed --> [*]
@enduml